                    <h4>About Kate</h4>
                    <p>An Atlanta native and College of Charleston graduate, Kate has six years combined experience with corporate events in weddings in New York City, Atlanta, and Charleston. After being an in house event coordinator for a popular event facility, Kate decided to take that knowledge to all of the exciting venues in Charleston. Kate Badger Special Events, LLC was formed in January, 2004 and produced twenty events the first year.</p>
                    <p>Thank you to all the friends, vendors, staff, and of course brides and grooms that have made this first year such a success!</p>
